           move      w-tes-tip-bil        to   rf-vbt-tip-bil         .
           move      w-tes-vdb-lv1        to   rf-vbt-vdb-lv1         .
           move      w-tes-vdb-lv2        to   rf-vbt-vdb-lv2         .
